# Notification Backend Standards

Trước khi code hoặc review bất kỳ thứ gì liên quan **Notification Service**, bắt buộc tuân thủ chuẩn backend chung (`.cursor/rules/social/social-backend-standards.mdc`) **và** toàn bộ quy tắc dưới đây. Source-of-truth nghiệp vụ: `docs/business-spec/notification-service-spec.md`.

## 1. Service Boundary

- **Own:** `notification_events`, `user_notifications`, `user_device_tokens`, `user_notification_settings`, delivery orchestration (in-app / push / email), retry workers.
- **PostgreSQL only** cho MVP (`notification_db`, port local **5435**). Không MongoDB.
- **Không** truy cập DB Auth/Social/Commerce/Admin. Chỉ lưu `user_id`, `actor_id`, `reference_id` (UUID/string) theo event payload hoặc JWT.
- **Không publish Outbox** từ Notification Service — service này là **consumer** domain events; producers là Auth/Social/Commerce/Admin.
- MVP ưu tiên **event payload đủ dữ liệu** để render notification; tránh synchronous lookup cross-service mỗi event.

## 2. Architecture & Package

Dependency flow: `delivery → application → domain → infrastructure` (không đảo chiều).

```
src/main/java/com/twohands/notification_service/
├── application/ingest/     # IngestNotificationEventUseCase
├── application/worker/     # Process, retry events/delivery
├── application/notification/  # In-app CRUD, settings, device token (khi có)
├── application/handler/    # Per event_type handlers (khuyến nghị)
├── delivery/http/          # User API + internal ingest
├── domain/                 # NotificationEvent, UserNotification, …
├── infrastructure/         # JPA, Kafka consumer, FCM, email, schedulers
├── config/ security/ exception/
```

**Use case naming:** `IngestNotificationEventUseCase`, `ProcessPendingNotificationEventsUseCase`, `ViewUserNotificationsUseCase` — không `NotificationService` generic.

**Forbidden (Notification):**
- Controller → repository trực tiếp.
- Business logic trong DTO/Controller.
- Expose JPA entity ra API.
- Gọi FCM/email **trong** DB transaction dài.
- Tin `title`/`content` raw từ producer — **template server-side** từ `event_type` + sanitized payload.
- Ack Kafka message **trước** khi persist `notification_events` thành công (hoặc dedup an toàn).
- Log full `device_token`, OTP, password reset token, provider API key.

## 3. API Contract

| Mục | Quy tắc |
|-----|---------|
| Base path (FR + spec §18) | `/notification/api/v1/{resource}` qua gateway; **trong service** scaffold hiện tại: `/api/v1/notification/...` — khi implement FR user API, **thống nhất một prefix** (ưu tiên path trong `FR_*.md`, cập nhật `SecurityConfig` cho khớp). |
| Local | `http://localhost:3004` (hoặc `SERVER_PORT=3005` nếu chạy song song `admin-service`) |
| Envelope | `docs/engineering_rules/api-standard.md` |
| Error prefix | `NOTIFICATION-*` (`ErrorCode` hiện có: `NOTIFICATION-400`, `NOTIFICATION-404`, `NOTIFICATION-409-DUPLICATE-EVENT`, …) |
| User APIs | JWT Bearer — user chỉ truy cập notification/settings/device token **của mình** |
| Internal ingest | `POST /api/v1/notification/internal/events` + header `X-Internal-Api-Key` (`NOTIFICATION_INTERNAL_API_KEY`); `permitAll` path + filter — **không** dùng user JWT |

**User API surface (MVP — spec §18 / FR):**

- `GET /notifications`, `GET /notifications/unread`, `GET /notifications/unread-count`
- `PATCH /notifications/{id}/read`, `PATCH /notifications/read-all`
- `DELETE /notifications/{id}` (soft delete: `is_deleted = true`)
- `GET /notification-settings`, `PUT /notification-settings/{eventType}`
- `POST /device-tokens`, `DELETE /device-tokens/{deviceToken}`

## 4. Domain State Machines (bắt buộc)

### notification_events

```text
PENDING → PROCESSING → COMPLETED
PENDING → PROCESSING → FAILED
FAILED → PROCESSING → COMPLETED | FAILED
```

- `processed_at` chỉ set khi `COMPLETED`.
- Idempotency: unique `(source_service, source_event_id)` khi `source_event_id` có giá trị; fallback `event_key` theo schema doc.

### user_notifications (in-app)

```text
CREATED (is_read=false) → READ (is_read=true, read_at set)
CREATED/READ → DELETED (is_deleted=true) — soft hide
```

### delivery_status (trên user_notifications — MVP)

```text
PENDING → SENT
PENDING → FAILED → SENT (sau retry thành công)
```

### user_device_tokens

- `device_token` unique; deactivate khi FCM báo invalid (không hard delete MVP trừ policy retention).

## 5. Event Ingestion & Processing Pipeline

```text
Broker / Internal API → Validate envelope → Dedup → INSERT notification_events (PENDING)
  → Worker (SKIP LOCKED) → PROCESSING → Handler(event_type)
    → Apply delivery rules + settings + skip-self
    → Create user_notifications / send push / send email
  → COMPLETED | FAILED (+ retry_count, last_error)
```

**Envelope tối thiểu** (`FR_ConsumeDomainEvent`, `event-ingestion-flow.md`):

- `event_id` (→ `source_event_id`), `event_type`, `source_service`, `payload`, `occurred_at`
- Optional: `event_key`, `aggregate_type`, `aggregate_id`, `actor_id`, `recipient_user_ids`

**source_service allowlist:** `AUTH`, `SOCIAL`, `COMMERCE`, `ADMIN`, `SYSTEM`.

**Event type:** `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`. Commerce có thể publish `COMMERCE_*` — handler phải **map alias** về canonical (vd: `COMMERCE_PAYMENT_PAID` → `PAYMENT_SUCCESS`) hoặc đăng ký cả hai.

## 6. Channel Routing Policy (MVP)

Áp dụng qua `FR_ApplyNotificationDeliveryRules` + `FR_RespectNotificationSettings`:

| Event type (canonical) | In-app | Push | Email |
|------------------------|:------:|:----:|:-----:|
| `POST_LIKED`, `USER_FOLLOWED`, `COMMENT_CREATED`, `COMMENT_REPLIED`, `COMMENT_LIKED` | yes | yes | no |
| `ORDER_CREATED`, `PAYMENT_SUCCESS` | yes | yes | yes |
| `PAYMENT_FAILED`, `SHIPMENT_*`, `ORDER_COMPLETED` | yes | yes | no |
| `EMAIL_VERIFICATION_REQUESTED`, `PASSWORD_RESET_REQUESTED` | no | no | yes |
| `USER_SUSPENDED`, `USER_RESTRICTED` | yes | yes | yes |
| `SYSTEM_ANNOUNCEMENT_SENT` / `PUBLISHED` | yes | optional | no |

**Critical override:** security/enforcement email có thể bypass user `allow_email=false` theo policy spec.

**Skip self** (`FR_SkipSelfNotification`): `actor_id == recipient_user_id` cho social events — không áp dụng payment/order/enforcement.

## 7. Consumed Events (producer → topic tham chiếu)

Notification **consume**, không sở hữu nghiệp vụ gốc:

| Producer | Event types (MVP) | Topic gợi ý (outbox resolver) |
|----------|-------------------|--------------------------------|
| Auth | `USER_CREATED`, `USER_UPDATED`, `USER_DELETED`, `EMAIL_VERIFICATION_REQUESTED`, `PASSWORD_RESET_REQUESTED`, `PASSWORD_CHANGED` | `auth.user.*`, `auth.email.*`, `auth.password.*` |
| Social | `POST_LIKED`, `COMMENT_CREATED`, `USER_FOLLOWED`, `COMMENT_REPLIED`, `COMMENT_LIKED` | `social.post.liked`, `social.comment.created`, `social.user.followed` |
| Commerce | `COMMERCE_ORDER_CREATED`, `COMMERCE_PAYMENT_PAID`, `COMMERCE_PAYMENT_FAILED`, `COMMERCE_SHIPMENT_*`, `COMMERCE_ORDER_COMPLETED`, … | `commerce.order.*`, `commerce.payment.*`, `commerce.shipment.*` |
| Admin | `USER_SUSPENDED`, `USER_BANNED`, `USER_RESTRICTED`, `POST_MODERATED`, `PRODUCT_REMOVED`, `REVIEW_HIDDEN`, `SHOP_SUSPENDED`, `SYSTEM_ANNOUNCEMENT_PUBLISHED`, … | `admin.user.*`, `admin.post.moderated`, `admin.announcement.*` |

Ma trận tổng hợp: `docs/architecture/event-driven-architecture.md` §4.

## 8. Data & Schema

- Schema doc: `docs/database/notification-schema.md`
- Migration: `Services/notification-service/src/main/resources/db/migration/V1__init_notification_tables.sql`
- PK UUID; timestamps `TIMESTAMPTZ`; payload `JSONB` sanitized.
- **Không** physical FK sang DB service khác.
- Unique: `(source_service, source_event_id)`, `(user_id, event_type)` settings, `device_token`.
- In-app list mặc định: `is_deleted = false`, sort `created_at DESC`, pagination bắt buộc.

## 9. Reliability & Idempotency

- At-least-once delivery → mọi handler **idempotent**.
- Cùng `source_event_id` → tối đa một `notification_events`.
- Cùng `(notification_event_id, user_id, type, reference_type, reference_id)` → không duplicate `user_notifications`.
- Worker: `FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED`, `locked_at`/`locked_by`, `max_retry_count`, backoff (`FR_RetryFailedNotificationEvents`).
- Push/email retry tách biệt (`FR_RetryFailedPushNotification`, `FR_RetryFailedEmailNotification`); invalid FCM token → deactivate, không retry vô hạn.

## 10. External Integrations

| Provider | Env | Ghi chú |
|----------|-----|---------|
| FCM | `NOTIFICATION_FCM_ENABLED=false` | Push; không log full token |
| Email (SMTP/SendGrid/…) | `NOTIFICATION_EMAIL_ENABLED=false` | Critical/system email only MVP |
| Kafka consumer | Chưa trong docker-compose mặc định | Dev: `POST /internal/events` hoặc bật consumer khi có broker |

## 11. Background Jobs (schedulers — tắt mặc định)

| Job | Env flag |
|-----|----------|
| Process pending events | `NOTIFICATION_PROCESS_EVENTS_ENABLED` |
| Retry failed events | `NOTIFICATION_RETRY_EVENTS_ENABLED` |
| Retry failed delivery | `NOTIFICATION_RETRY_DELIVERY_ENABLED` |
| Cleanup invalid device tokens | `FR_CleanupInvalidDeviceToken` |
| Cleanup old notifications | `FR_CleanupOldNotifications` (optional) |
| Review reminder | `FR_SendReviewReminderNotification` (optional) |

Cron/batch: `application.yml` → `notification.workers.*`.

## 12. Local Development

```bash
cd Infrastructure && docker compose up -d postgres-notification redis
cd Services/notification-service && cp .env.example .env
```

- `DB_URL=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5435/notification_db`
- `JWT_ACCESS_SECRET` / `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET` ≥32 chars, **cùng auth-service**
- `SERVER_PORT=3005` nếu `admin-service` đang dùng 3004
- Workers/FCM/Email: để `false` cho dev ingest-only

Chạy: `./gradlew bootRun` · Health: `GET /actuator/health`, `GET /api/v1/notification/health`

## 13. Security & Privacy

- JWT: `user_id` từ token, không tin query/body cho ownership.
- Internal ingest: API key filter trước JWT filter.
- Sanitize `payload`/`metadata` trước log và trước trả FE.
- Notification content không lộ chi tiết private vượt quyền recipient — deep link qua `reference_type` + `reference_id`; resource vẫn authorize ở owner service.
- Không log: password, OTP, refresh token, full device token, email provider secret.

## 14. Testing

- Unit: idempotency ingest, skip-self, delivery rules, handler routing, template rendering.
- Integration: ingest API, process worker + DB, user notification API ownership.
- Cấu trúc: `src/test/java/.../unit/`, `.../integration/`

## 15. MVP Out of Scope

WebSocket realtime, marketing campaigns, per-channel delivery table (trừ khi cần debug), notification analytics, multi-language template engine, websocket cluster — xem spec §22.

